  <div class="comment_content">
	<div class="comment_body">
	  CL-FAD ライブラリの walk-directory 関数を使ってます。
	</div>
	
	
	
    <div class="compact">
      <table><tr><td class="linenos"><pre>1
2
3
4
5
6</pre></td><td class="code"><div class="highlight"><pre>(defun remove-backup ()
  (let ((str (or (pathname-type path) (pathname-name path))))
    (when (char= #\~ (char str (1- (length str))))
      (delete-file path))))

(fad:walk-directory ディレクトリ名 #&#39;remove-backup)
</pre></div>
</td></tr></table>
    </div>
	

  
